ned empty.\n   - Fix: Add `login_cubit_test.dart`, `matching_socket_cubit_test.d
art`, and extend `matching_bloc_test.dart`.\n\n**Major Issues:**\n3. **Fly-off a
nimation broken for button press and drag release** - `_onSwipeActionSubmitted` 
sets `_animation` to offset 500 but emits `MatchingSwipeInProgress`, not the ani
mation state. The nested `BlocBuilder` only rebuilds on `MatchingSwipeAnimation`
