t.dart`, not in `home_page.dart`.\n   - Fix: Remove unused event/handler, or wir
e it up if needed.\n\n**Minor Issues:**\n6. `_onSwipeAnimationCompleted` is decl
ared `async` but doesn't `await` anything.\n7. `MatchingSocketCubit` double-emit
pattern could cause unnecessary rebuilds.\n8. The PR claims `flutter test` passe
d but didn't add tests for new code - the 38 tests are all pre-existing.\n\n**Di
mension checks:**\n- **功能完整性**: The core separation is implemented for Logi
nPage and HomePage. But the matching swipe animation functionality is broken (re
gression). Also mode persistence on retry is broken.\n- **代码规范性**: Generall
y good. But dead code exists. Naming follows conventions.\n- **测试覆盖**: ❌ Mi
ssing tests for new Cubits and new Bloc events.\n- **文档同步**: ✅ Docs updated
